---
description: Run build and type check, fix any errors
allowed-tools: [Read, Edit, Bash, Glob, Grep]
---

Run build and type validation.

## Tasks

1. Verify `.env.example` exists
   - If missing, search code for `process.env` and auto-generate `.env.example`
   - If exists, check for missing keys

2. ESLint check
   ```bash
   npx next lint
   ```
   - Fix errors (warnings can be ignored)
   - If `eslint.config.mjs` or `.eslintrc.json` doesn't exist, proceed with defaults

3. Run npm run build
   - Fix any errors
   - Rebuild after fixes

4. Type check with npx tsc --noEmit
   - Fix any type errors

5. Confirm build success after all errors resolved

6. Run /self-review on successful build
